# dictionaryRepresentation()

**Instance Method**

Returns the contents of a diagnostic as a dictionary.

## Declaration

```swift
func dictionaryRepresentation() -> [AnyHashable : Any]
```

## Return Value

A [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Swift/Dictionary] (Swift) or [doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/Foundation/NSDictionary] (Objective-C) object containing the JSON representation of the contents of the diagnostic.

## Generating a report

- **jsonRepresentation()**: Returns the contents of the diagnostic in JSON format.
